section.section:
Members of the nominating commission shall serve four (4) year terms, or until a successor shall be appointed, except the initial appointments shall be as follows:
One (1) member shall serve a one (1) year term;
Two (2) members shall serve a two (2) year term;
One (1) member shall serve a three (3) year term; and
One (1) member shall serve a four (4) year term.
